# Country Website ğŸŒ

This is a simple country information website built using **React.js**.  
It shows details of different countries using data from a public API.

The project is made for learning React concepts like components, routing, API calls, and state management.

ğŸ”— Live Website:  
https://YOUR-NETLIFY-LINK.netlify.app

